title: Ep. - 205 - COURTNEY FROM 90 DAY FIANCE: THE OTHER WAY AND BIKRAM YOGA DOC REVIEW
description:
EPISODE 205

COURTNEY FROM 90 DAY FIANCE: THE OTHER WAY AND BIKRAM YOGA DOC REVIEW


Producer and podcast host Aliza Rosen reviews the new Netflix documentary Bikram: Yogi, Guru, Predator, following the rise and fall of Bikram yoga founder Bikram Choudhury.


Kate interviews Courtney from 90 Day Fiance: The Other Way, a show about Americans moving across the globe for the person they love.


Reality Life with Kate Casey
